    "In generating content for traffic safety education and publicity, it can create diverse materials and interactive platforms to increase public awareness and understanding.",
    "The application of AIGC in road network design and planning enables road planners to generate optimal design solutions and quickly simulate traffic flow performance under different scenarios, assessing each option's advantages and disadvantages.",
    "This helps select the most efficient and cost-effective solution.",
    "AIGC can also generate road network optimization recommendations based on historical data and real-time demand, such as adding or optimizing road nodes and adjusting lane configurations, to improve network capacity.",
    "In urban transportation, road network planning is closely related to the Network Design Problem (NDP) (Bagloee et al., 2017)."
